movies.title: Kuzpups the Musical
movies.plot: Kuzpups the Musical is a Kuzkid Original movie about Roscoe, Missy, Pippin and Oliver (Kuzpups) that go on an adventure to return the Golden Dog Treat to Mount Naws. As the four pups travel on their journey, they mix in many original songs created by the Director and CEO of Kuzkid, Dale Gray.
